        "body": "## Summary\n- add create/update validation for announce delivery when channel is Feishu/Lark\n- require non-empty `delivery.to` so invalid jobs fail fast at creation time\n- add regression tests for missing-target rejection and explicit-target acceptance\n\n## Why\n`cron add --announce --channel feishu` could create jobs without `delivery.to`, which only fail at runtime. This moves the failure to create-time.\n\nCloses #39599\n\n## Testing\n- `pnpm test:fast -- src/cron/service.jobs.test.ts` (target suite passed; unrelated existing failures remain in wider suite)\n",
